summary: This module defines integration tests that set up a temporary local feature store repository, load synthetic driver data, configure entities and feature views, materialize the data to the online store, and verify that online feature retrieval returns the expected values, including scenarios with partial materialization.
business_intent: Validate the end-to-end functionality of the local feature store implementation, ensuring that data can be ingested, materialized, and served online correctly for downstream machine learning applications.
